Package: groupedHyperframe
Nickname: Entertaining-but-Useless
Type: Package
Title: Grouped Hyper Data Frame
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2026-03-24
Description: An S3 class 'groupedHyperframe' that inherits from 
    the hyper data frame class from the 'spatstat' packages. 
    Batch process and aggregation of the hyper column(s) 
    over a nested grouping structure.  
    Active development of this R package is temporarily suspended. 
    Until further notice, it should not be used as a basis 
    for research grant applications or cited as an actively maintained tool.
